meta.description: Library for multiprecision complex arithmetic with exact rounding

license.fullName: GNU Library General Public License v2 or later

meta.long_description:
GNU MPC is a C library for the arithmetic of complex numbers with
        arbitrarily high precision and correct rounding of the result.  It is
        built upon and follows the same principles as GNU MPFR.
meta.name: libmpc
